c: 9
v: 114
t: "Futhi kwakungesikhona nje ukuthi u-Abrahamu wacelela uyise intethelelo ngaphandle kokuthi kwakuyisethembiso ayemthembise sona kepha kwathi lapho sekumcacele (u-Abrahamu) ukuthi (uyise) uyisitha sikaMvelinqangi waqhelelana\tnaye,\tngempela\tu-Abrahamu\twayeqotho ekukhonzeni uMvelinqangi ebekezela"